20:20.753 --> 20:21.720 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: The failure?

20:21.754 --> 20:23.289 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

20:23.322 --> 20:25.324 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BERNIE SANDERS: Yes, which is
