22:05.291 --> 22:06.258 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
BERNIE SANDERS: It's not good.

22:06.292 --> 22:07.259 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Not good.

22:07.293 --> 22:09.094 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Not good, and not surprising,
