23:18.464 --> 23:19.865 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
People see through that.

23:19.898 --> 23:22.234 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, I think the Democratic Party
has got to
make fundamental choices.

23:22.268 --> 23:25.604 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
