23:59.371 --> 24:06.145 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Now, this is not just a stupid
expression,
but it is incredibly dangerous.

24:06.178 --> 24:09.782 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The other area where there is no
compromise
