24:09.815 --> 24:15.020 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We have struggled too much, too
long as a
country trying to overcome
racism and sexism

24:15.054 --> 24:16.155 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
and homophobia.

24:16.188 --> 24:19.425 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We cannot go back to a more
discriminatory
society.

24:19.458 --> 24:21.593 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So, those are issues where there
is no compromise.

24:21.627 --> 24:25.931 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
On the other hand, as somebody
