companies, changing
our trade policies, rebuilding
the infrastructure.

26:50.676 --> 26:52.511 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Trump talked about taking on
Wall Street.

26:52.544 --> 26:54.446 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Well, we are going to hold him
accountable.

26:54.480 --> 26:58.350 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
